000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Think about which word labels a person.","textBn":"ভাবুন কোন শব্দটি একজন ব্যক্তিকে চিহ্নিত করে।"},{"id":"d620a39e-b0eb-4fb1-845e-72616d33e7cf","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"A goodbye is what you say when you leave.","textBn":"বিদায় হলো চলে যাওয়ার সময় যা বলা হয়।"},{"id":"be3a81cd-6f16-4f52-bcb5-5130547ce033","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Start with the verb: \"See you …\".","textBn":"ক্রিয়া দিয়ে শুরু করুন: \"See you …\"।"},{"id":"fa065fd4-3529-4058-9452-a677f23ac810","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000020","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"ARTICLE","textEn":"Bengali has no a/an/the — English needs an article before most singular nouns.","textBn":"বাংলায় a/an/the নেই — ইংরেজিতে বেশিরভাগ একবচন বিশেষ্যের আগে একটি আর্টিকেল লাগে।"},{"id":"9ea611dd-bff2-4515-85a4-d946040788ec","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000020","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Use \"an\" before a vowel sound (a, e, i, o, u).","textBn":"স্বরধ্বনির (a, e, i, o, u) আগে \"an\" ব্যবহার করুন।"},{"id":"51c9baad-b927-4daa-8832-26bc76bbaab8","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000021","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"the","textEn":"Use \"a\" here — \"the\" is for something specific.","textBn":"এখানে \"a\" ব্যবহার করুন — নির্দিষ্ট কিছুর জন্য \"the\" হয়।"},{"id":"77dc0082-8fb6-4b8c-870e-e6fff46342ad","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000021","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"ARTICLE","textEn":"A single, general thing takes \"a\" (consonant sound) or \"an\" (vowel sound).","textBn":"একটি সাধারণ জিনিসের আগে \"a\" (ব্যঞ্জনধ্বনি) বা \"an\" (স্বরধ্বনি) বসে।"},{"id":"5ed7565b-8504-4c51-89fa-fb8da23b37ac","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000021","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Use \"a\" before a consonant sound.","textBn":"ব্যঞ্জনধ্বনির আগে \"a\" ব্যবহার করুন।"},{"id":"d9c4c799-2037-4793-8b9c-592342cc3859","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000022","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"ARTICLE","textEn":"Job titles take an article: \"a doctor\", \"an engineer\".","textBn":"পেশার নামের আগে আর্টিকেল বসে: \"a doctor\", \"an engineer\"।"},{"id":"93475d20-c7ea-47b1-af05-f0759d1159f6","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000022","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Order: person + is + a + job. → \"She is a doctor\".","textBn":"ক্রম: ব্যক্তি + is + a + পেশা। → \"She is a doctor\"।"},{"id":"887c8979-fc59-40ba-b0a3-5884fbc55e36","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000030","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"ARTICLE","textEn":"Use \"the\" for a unique thing everyone knows — like the sun.","textBn":"সবাই চেনে এমন অনন্য জিনিসের জন্য \"the\" ব্যবহার করুন — যেমন the sun।"},{"id":"5878507d-c17c-4927-97c1-1ac6db62e986","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000030","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"There is only one sun, so it takes \"the\".","textBn":"সূর্য একটাই, তাই এর আগে \"the\" বসে।"},{"id":"b900b4fd-abb0-4c76-a4b6-73e6022c3921","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000031","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"A command starts with the verb: \"Open …\".","textBn":"আদেশ ক্রিয়া দিয়ে শুরু হয়: \"Open …\"।"},{"id":"cddf3763-0de8-4a83-b584-69797964e9d2","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000040","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"COPULA","textEn":"English keeps the \"to be\" verb — with \"I\" it is always \"am\".","textBn":"ইংরেজিতে \"to be\" ক্রিয়া থাকে — \"I\"-এর সাথে সবসময় \"am\"।"},{"id":"ddb230a1-af4f-4750-96f2-f154b735b1a3","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000040","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"With \"I\", use \"am\".","textBn":"\"I\"-এর সাথে \"am\" ব্যবহার করুন।"},{"id":"d53ed016-7c52-462c-97f5-20ae69542af4","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"i student","textEn":"Add the verb and the article: \"I am a student\".","textBn":"ক্রিয়া ও আর্টিকেল যোগ করুন: \"I am a student\"।"},{"id":"083010d7-8bd9-42bc-92b3-b2b835294b38","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"i a student","textEn":"Almost — add the verb \"am\": \"I am a student\".","textBn":"প্রায় ঠিক — \"am\" ক্রিয়াটি যোগ করুন: \"I am a student\"।"},{"id":"663f4356-b629-4d7f-8295-31a2a37b1147","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"COPULA","textEn":"Bengali drops \"to be\", but English needs it — use am/is/are.","textBn":"বাংলায় \"to be\" বাদ পড়ে, কিন্তু ইংরেজিতে তা লাগে — am/is/are ব্যবহার করুন।"},{"id":"24dca377-9a5c-4426-8da9-b7a7bfdad1c7","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000041","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Remember the verb \"am\" and the article \"a\".","textBn":"\"am\" ক্রিয়া ও \"a\" আর্টিকেলটি মনে রাখুন।"},{"id":"7b5059cf-d470-400f-bc26-03aa241173f2","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000042","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"With \"You\", use \"are\": \"You are …\".","textBn":"\"You\"-এর সাথে \"are\" ব্যবহার করুন: \"You are …\"।"},{"id":"bb6b37cc-2c8c-46ba-91d0-f6de422af3a5","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000050","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"COPULA","textEn":"With he / she / it, the \"to be\" verb is \"is\".","textBn":"he / she / it-এর সাথে \"to be\" ক্রিয়াটি হলো \"is\"।"},{"id":"51207ada-6b20-4530-9e99-cfa1533723c7","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000050","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"With \"She\", use \"is\".","textBn":"\"She\"-এর সাথে \"is\" ব্যবহার করুন।"},{"id":"b0159016-c8ac-4800-9669-b49605c029f3","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000051","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"are","textEn":"\"He\" is singular — use \"is\", not \"are\".","textBn":"\"He\" একবচন — \"are\" নয়, \"is\" ব্যবহার করুন।"},{"id":"4b450c29-49f4-4044-878d-abfc8508946a","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000051","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"COPULA","textEn":"Do not drop the verb — \"He is tall\", not \"He tall\".","textBn":"ক্রিয়া বাদ দেবেন না — \"He tall\" নয়, \"He is tall\"।"},{"id":"f0188589-ebfa-4c62-ac34-95d113770387","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000051","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"With \"He\", use \"is\".","textBn":"\"He\"-এর সাথে \"is\" ব্যবহার করুন।"},{"id":"7d1d200e-39fd-43ec-a06e-66bfdb989cda","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000060","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PLURAL","textEn":"For more than one, English adds \"-s\": book → books.","textBn":"একাধিক বোঝাতে ইংরেজিতে \"-s\" যোগ হয়: book → books।"},{"id":"66d6d033-12a4-49f2-b045-c1fd1ca8e6a9","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000060","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Two or more of something takes \"-s\".","textBn":"কোনো কিছু দুই বা তার বেশি হলে \"-s\" বসে।"},{"id":"89992760-c06e-4ead-b79a-512da31775d4","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000061","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"cat","textEn":"More than one — add \"-s\": \"cats\".","textBn":"একাধিক — \"-s\" যোগ করুন: \"cats\"।"},{"id":"bfee628e-48ea-408a-9a5f-22b500bcdb8c","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000061","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PLURAL","textEn":"After a number bigger than one, the noun is plural: \"three cats\".","textBn":"একের বেশি সংখ্যার পরে বিশেষ্যটি বহুবচন হয়: \"three cats\"।"},{"id":"40f90152-2482-4d10-bb52-03b0e177c3c0","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000061","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Add \"-s\" to make the plural of \"cat\".","textBn":"\"cat\"-এর বহুবচন করতে \"-s\" যোগ করুন।"},{"id":"b019baf5-b6b7-4a1b-af87-34fa1c6407e5","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000062","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PLURAL","textEn":"The number \"two\" needs the plural noun \"books\", not \"book\".","textBn":"\"two\" সংখ্যার সাথে বহুবচন \"books\" লাগে, \"book\" নয়।"},{"id":"c214b7f9-6f6f-431d-8b15-8e806f5b7290","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000062","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Order: I + have + two + books.","textBn":"ক্রম: I + have + two + books।"},{"id":"66aa999b-8a78-43e1-85b4-d2ee60312954","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000063","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PLURAL","textEn":"Some plurals are irregular — no \"-s\": child → children.","textBn":"কিছু বহুবচন অনিয়মিত — \"-s\" ছাড়া: child → children।"},{"id":"1da5f27a-ced7-411b-9d48-e56977b0ce1c","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000063","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"The plural of \"child\" is \"children\".","textBn":"\"child\"-এর বহুবচন \"children\"।"},{"id":"73130595-b2a0-4cbe-8312-9a25c8887593","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000064","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PLURAL","textEn":"Irregular plural: the vowel changes — man → men.","textBn":"অনিয়মিত বহুবচন: স্বরধ্বনি বদলায় — man → men।"},{"id":"9ba97186-cc40-4f63-9f10-86d98a315fa7","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000064","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"The plural of \"man\" is \"men\".","textBn":"\"man\"-এর বহুবচন \"men\"।"},{"id":"9ff62ec5-76c3-4452-8062-c0a2cf90a57c","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000070","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PREPOSITION","textEn":"Use \"on\" for a surface — something rests on top of the table.","textBn":"কোনো তলের জন্য \"on\" ব্যবহার করুন — কিছু টেবিলের উপরে থাকে।"},{"id":"30ccc7ab-86bd-4d49-964f-dd255e3bb65f","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000070","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"On top of a surface → \"on\".","textBn":"কোনো তলের উপরে → \"on\"।"},{"id":"27c8b73e-e607-421d-a83a-63addb6cb5bb","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000071","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PREPOSITION","textEn":"Use \"in\" for a city or country: \"in Dhaka\", \"in Bangladesh\".","textBn":"শহর বা দেশের জন্য \"in\": \"in Dhaka\", \"in Bangladesh\"।"},{"id":"d982e24d-006e-483d-8444-a3a776ce5fc9","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000071","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"A city takes \"in\".","textBn":"শহরের জন্য \"in\" বসে।"},{"id":"be3dd482-9607-4907-a7c6-6ca4204127bc","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000072","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PREPOSITION","textEn":"Inside a container → \"in\": the cat is in the box.","textBn":"কোনো পাত্রের ভেতরে → \"in\": the cat is in the box।"},{"id":"e8379dd8-1579-4ece-9425-0fe7036ade4d","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000072","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Order: The + cat + is + in + the + box.","textBn":"ক্রম: The + cat + is + in + the + box।"},{"id":"0cd122b5-121b-45c5-812f-4f3096136652","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000073","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PREPOSITION","textEn":"Use \"at\" for a clock time: \"at 7 o'clock\", \"at noon\".","textBn":"ঘড়ির সময়ের জন্য \"at\": \"at 7 o'clock\", \"at noon\"।"},{"id":"5f84cf1f-cae4-48d9-801a-61bf1aa5c4ca","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000073","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"A clock time takes \"at\".","textBn":"ঘড়ির সময়ের জন্য \"at\" বসে।"},{"id":"d56e6528-be11-4120-95a8-620dec566d0e","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000074","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"on","textEn":"For a month, use \"in\", not \"on\": \"in July\".","textBn":"মাসের জন্য \"on\" নয়, \"in\": \"in July\"।"},{"id":"1c1bc5af-7853-4120-9dca-e793a5da9427","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000074","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"PREPOSITION","textEn":"Use \"in\" for months and years: \"in July\", \"in 2026\".","textBn":"মাস ও বছরের জন্য \"in\": \"in July\", \"in 2026\"।"},{"id":"666929e0-1d41-4d0f-b4b7-3925a7d8e884","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000074","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"A month takes \"in\".","textBn":"মাসের জন্য \"in\" বসে।"},{"id":"b8c4a953-cee1-4914-bf51-dd43a8d22d04","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000080","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"\"Eat\" is what you do with food.","textBn":"খাবার নিয়ে যা করা হয় তা হলো \"eat\"।"},{"id":"dfd752ae-f5d4-4afa-8db9-f426d16fcc8e","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000081","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"\"Go\" means to move to another place.","textBn":"\"Go\" মানে অন্য জায়গায় যাওয়া।"},{"id":"a985e591-43b4-4d92-8558-f6c6f19ad061","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000082","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"i drink","textEn":"Say what you drink: \"I drink water\".","textBn":"আপনি কী পান করেন তা বলুন: \"I drink water\"।"},{"id":"309f22cb-c01b-4f34-aed0-be227fb5cf04","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000082","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Order: I + drink + water.","textBn":"ক্রম: I + drink + water।"},{"id":"3440c8e8-a3dc-4297-a9ab-5b4e63c962b9","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000083","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Order: subject + verb + a + noun. → \"I read a book\".","textBn":"ক্রম: কর্তা + ক্রিয়া + a + বিশেষ্য। → \"I read a book\"।"},{"id":"f21c87e7-03e7-4f80-a76a-941ecea6a965","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000084","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"VERB_S","textEn":"In the present simple, he / she / it takes a verb ending in \"-s\".","textBn":"Present simple-এ he / she / it-এর ক্রিয়ার শেষে \"-s\" বসে।"},{"id":"4d4336d5-501e-4161-b1c6-8f77228cca62","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000084","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"With \"She\", the verb is \"eats\".","textBn":"\"She\"-এর সাথে ক্রিয়াটি \"eats\"।"},{"id":"901f903d-e020-4485-82b1-52047b453490","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000085","trigger":"WRONG_ANSWER","triggerKey":"go","textEn":"\"He\" needs the \"-s\" form — and \"go\" becomes \"goes\".","textBn":"\"He\"-এর জন্য \"-s\" রূপ লাগে — আর \"go\" হয় \"goes\"।"},{"id":"b305be4e-f3a3-456e-b94d-eada918d8d44","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000085","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"VERB_S","textEn":"For he / she / it, \"go\" becomes \"goes\" (add -es after o).","textBn":"he / she / it-এর জন্য \"go\" হয় \"goes\" (o-এর পরে -es যোগ হয়)।"},{"id":"0aba4422-51f2-4d7b-940e-84213a22d934","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000085","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"The he/she/it form of \"go\" is \"goes\".","textBn":"\"go\"-এর he/she/it রূপ হলো \"goes\"।"},{"id":"b548a34e-1664-469f-914e-c74e153f62a8","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000086","trigger":"PATTERN","triggerKey":"VERB_S","textEn":"\"She\" takes the \"-s\" verb: \"drinks\", not \"drink\".","textBn":"\"She\"-এর সাথে \"-s\" যুক্ত ক্রিয়া বসে: \"drink\" নয়, \"drinks\"।"},{"id":"b73000c0-3340-42bb-b27a-ad930674a006","exerciseId":"50000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000086","trigger":"DEFAULT","triggerKey":null,"textEn":"Order: She + drinks + tea.","textBn":"ক্রম: She + drinks + tea।"}]}